name: Checking a date via date picker using calendar module
fullName: features/ui/widget_interactions_with_input_fields.feature#Checking a date via date picker using calendar module

steps.name: I navigate to Demoqa Home page
Given I navigate to Date Picker page
When I select "12/23/2024/17:00" in Date And Time calendar
Then the date picked is "December 23, 2024 5:00 PM" in the field
